sources.description:
Queen . . . of a Crime Cult !
A convicted thief in Dartmoor prison hides the location of the stolen Bank of England printing plates inside three music boxes. When the innocent purchasers of the boxes start to be murdered, Holmes and Watson investigate.

Original title: Dressed to Kill (1946) AKA: Prelude to Murder/Sherlock Holmes and the Secret Code

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/f46uuHG6SYw

Available with dubbed audio in German, Italian & Spanish. And also subtitled in more than 30+ languages. Click on ⚙️ and choose subtitles and/or audio tracks.

Director: Roy William Neill
Writers: Arthur Conan Doyle, Leonard Lee, Frank Gruber
Cast: Basil Rathbone, Nigel Bruce, Patricia Morison 
Genre:  Colorized classics, Crime, Mystery
